column5: While visiting my son for his residency graduation I seen this mail box set up......do you think this could be a Redneck Mail Box.....
Maybe the young,ns get the mail for granny.  Then again,it might me a tree stand for hunt,n squirls.
Brian.........I like that.........for the young'ns.......good foresight....
I like the tree stand for huntin Squirrels better
